menuItem.name: Blonde Roast
menuItem.description: Lightly roasted coffee that's soft, mellow and flavorful. Easy-drinking on its own and delicious with milk, sugar or flavored with vanilla, caramel or hazelnut.

menuItem.name: Caffe Misto
menuItem.description: A one-to-one mix of fresh brewed coffee and steamed milk add up to one distinctly delicious coffee drink.

menuItem.name: Iced Coffee
menuItem.description: Freshly brewed Starbushe Iced Coffee Blend served chilled and lightly sweetened over ice.

menuItem.name: Iced Coffee with Milk
menuItem.description: Freshly brewed Starbushe Iced Coffee Blend with milk – served chilled and lightly sweetened over ice

menuItem.name: Vanilla Sweet Cream Cold Brew
menuItem.description: Just before serving, our slow-steeped custom blend Narino 70 Cold Brew is topped with a delicate float of house-made vanilla sweet cream that cascades throughout the cup.

menuItem.name: Ancho Chipotle Chicken
menuItem.description: We slow cook shredded chicken breast in warm spices, then add a thick ancho-chipotle sauce, fire-roasted poblano peppers, red onion and three-chili gouda cheese. Top this off with spicy cilantro pesto and serve it on an artisan-style ciabatta bread, and you're ready to savor a taste of the southwest.

menuItem.name: Egg Salad Sandwich
menuItem.description: Egg salad mixed with chives, dill relish and arugula on cider wheat bread.

menuItem.name: Spinach, Feta & Cage Free Egg White Breakfast Wrap
menuItem.description: We bring together cage-free egg whites, spinach, feta cheese and tomatoes inside a whole wheat wrap, then toast it to perfection. Vegetarian and protein-rich, this low calorie wrap is a tasty start to any morning.

menuItem.name: Hearty Blueberry Oatmeal
menuItem.description: A blend of rolled and steel-cut oats with blueberries and agave syrup.

menuItem.name: Bacon, Gouda & Egg Breakfast Sandwich
menuItem.description: Sizzling Applewood smoked bacon, melty aged Gouda and a parmesan frittata are layered on an artisan roll for extra smoky breakfast goodness.

menuItem.name: Chonga Bagel
menuItem.description: A bagel topped with Cheddar cheese, poppy seeds, sesame seeds, onion and garlic.

menuItem.name: Butter Croissant
menuItem.description: This classic Croissant is made with 100 percent butter to create a golden, crunchy top and soft, flakey layers inside. The perfect match for a cup of Pike Place Roast.

menuItem.name: Chocolate Chunk Muffin
menuItem.description: Our moist, muffin is mixed with four (that’s right, four) different Colombian single-origin chocolates, including a milk chocolate and 3 unique semi-sweet chocolates. Craving chocolate, anyone?

menuItem.name: Devil's Food Doughnut
menuItem.description: A classic glazed chocolate cake doughnut.

menuItem.name: Pumpkin Cheesecake Bar
menuItem.description: A honey graham crust baked with pumpkin gingerbread bursting with candied ginger, real pumpkin, cinnamon and nutmeg, topped with creamy Chicago-style cheesecake made with slow-cultured cream cheese and sour cream, finished with a swirl of lightly-spiced pumpkin cheesecake.
